column3: “This is a fun strain to consume in casual situations with friends, but in my experience would prefer not to use when work is needed to be done or focus is required. When conversing with others there was a tendency during t...”

This strain is different from the ones I've ...”

column5: and the OG doesn't defer too long before relaxation begins. I recommend this strain for late afternoon pick-me-ups

column3: “Hands down, my favorite strain and I've tried a lot.  It's a preference but it's also because it's so damn good.  I enjoy the overall experience -- taste, smoke, smell, buzz, medicinal effects -- when smoking Deadhead" OG Kush."  I use primarily to get a good night's sleep.  There's no other strain that works better for getting really good sound sleep.  It's also great for just unwinding after a long day.  It really...”"

“Wipes out the negative parts of your brain while leaving in tact - and even amplifying - the right parts. By that I mean, you almost autonomously accomplish what you need despite feeling like the brain’s ability to make that happen has been scooped right out. There’s an overriding mental stupor that makes actively thinking or concentrating on things impossible, but that doesn’t stop you from doing what you need at a ...”

“I love this strain. It was pretty potent, even for my high tolerance. Amazing pain relief, and definitely a night time med because it knocked me out! No real downsides, other than the normal dry mouth and munchies. Easy to hold in, and not a taste that's bad enough to keep you away from it. (again, I'm not a smoker who can appreciate the taste or smell.) Definitly a good strain!!!”

“A pleasant, mild, clear headed high.  Choose if you're in the mood to be fully functional and high as well.  Would probably be a nice  intro strain for your friends who are new to cannabis.”

“Maybe the best strain for migraine sufferers...Girlfriend gets chronic and this is her favorite for stopping an oncoming or making a migraine go away.    Food coma and sleep kicked in and put me in full zombie mode. This is not a day time green if you have shit to do.
